Basically the purpose of music extention is to let those kids experience what it would be like to be a performer, or composer, or musicologist so they can take that further.

00:00:42.540 --> 00:00:49.840
They can go to university or TAFE or some of them might just choose to continue playing and loving music after school, which is really what we are here for.

00:00:50.090 --> 00:00:54.000
Year 8s can choose arts, dance, drama Music.  They get a term each - a bit of a taster.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:04.050
Right through to Year 12 where you know we offer things like music extention, we've got fashion design, design, media studies, music studies - there's basically every subject that you would want to do.

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:16.000
We've just bought some MacBook Pros and the kids get the opportunity to create movies, they can film in the blue screen, in After Effects and there's so many opportunities for kids.  Its really fantastic, some of the work they are producing

