00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:36.870
So start on the bottom and drag up.  We're just trying to make it as smooth as we can.

00:01:37.210 --> 00:01:44.630
As you can see behind us here, this is the Year 11 construction class. Each student is completing a Certificate 1 in construction.

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:50.980
They are achieving this by working in conjunction with an organisation known as CSQ, Which stands for Construction Skills Queensland.

00:01:52.350 --> 00:02:01.250
My role's is one of mentoring first and foremost. We interview the students in Year 10 to become part of our Doorways to Construction Program.

00:02:01.250 --> 00:02:09.490
And a big part of the Program is putting them out on work placement. And the idea behind that is we give them a taste of the trade they want to be.

00:02:09.950 --> 00:02:14.500
I am hoping to try and get a school-based apprenticeship in my work placement.

00:02:14.570 --> 00:02:16.740
Love your work. Thanks guys.

