The subjects I'm taking currently at Forest Lake State High School help me decide on what I want to be when I'm older, as well as choose my university subjects and degree.

00:05:01.400 --> 00:05:10.570
What I think make Forest Lake State High School special is that no matter who you are or where you come from there's just this general sense of equality and positive engery within our learning envirnoment.

